The paper deals with image processing, text extraction, and keyword identification, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions language identification (cs.CL) and on-device computation (cs.LG), which are relevant sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with mobile screenshots, which can be considered as a form of multimedia (cs.MM).
